    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_notu] AS [t8]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]
) AS [s0] ON [s].[id] = [s0].[is_emri_id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t10].[id], [t10].[aciklama], [t10].[degisim_tarihi], [t10].[durum_id], [t10].[is_emri_id], [t10].[kullanici_id], [t10].[olusturma_tarihi], [t11].[id] AS [id0], [t11].[ad], [t11].[aktif], [t11].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t11].[renk], [t11].[sira], [t12].[id] AS [id1], [t12].[ad_soyad], [t12].[aktif] AS [aktif0], [t12].[dukkan_id], [t12].[email], [t12].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi1], [t12].[rol], [t12].[sifre_hash], [t12].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_durum_gecmisi] AS [t10]

    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t12] ON [t10].[kullanici_id] = [t12].[id]
) AS [s1] ON [s].[id] = [s1].[is_emri_id]

2026-01-02 21:11:26.655 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@dukkanId='?' (DbType = Guid), @p='?' (DbType = Int32), @p0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t1].[id], [t1].[is_emri_no], [t1].[dukkan_id], [t1].[musteri_id], COALESCE([t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi], N''), [t0].[telefon], [t1].[cihaz_id], [t3].[marka] + N' ' + [t3].[model], [t2].[seri_no], [t1].[durum_id], [t4].[ad], [t4].[renk], [t1].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t1].[oncelik], [t1].[tahmini_ucret], [t1].[olusturma_tarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

) AS [t1]

    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]

    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]

) AS [s]

    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]

    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t4] ON [t3].[kategori_id] = [t4].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t5] ON [t].[durum_id] = [t5].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_notu] AS [t8]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]
) AS [s0] ON [s].[id] = [s0].[is_emri_id]
LEFT JOIN (

    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t12] ON [t10].[kullanici_id] = [t12].[id]
) AS [s1] ON [s].[id] = [s1].[is_emri_id]

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]

    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]

INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]

ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

SELECT [t1].[id], [t1].[is_emri_no], [t1].[dukkan_id], [t1].[musteri_id], COALESCE([t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi], N''), [t0].[telefon], [t1].[cihaz_id], [t3].[marka] + N' ' + [t3].[model], [t2].[seri_no], [t1].[durum_id], [t4].[ad], [t4].[renk], [t1].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t1].[oncelik], [t1].[tahmini_ucret], [t1].[olusturma_tarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

SELECT [t1].[id], [t1].[is_emri_no], [t1].[dukkan_id], [t1].[musteri_id], COALESCE([t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi], N''), [t0].[telefon], [t1].[cihaz_id], [t3].[marka] + N' ' + [t3].[model], [t2].[seri_no], [t1].[durum_id], [t4].[ad], [t4].[renk], [t1].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t1].[oncelik], [t1].[tahmini_ucret], [t1].[olusturma_tarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]

) AS [s]

) AS [t1]

SELECT [t1].[id], [t1].[is_emri_no], [t1].[dukkan_id], [t1].[musteri_id], COALESCE([t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi], N''), [t0].[telefon], [t1].[cihaz_id], [t3].[marka] + N' ' + [t3].[model], [t2].[seri_no], [t1].[durum_id], [t4].[ad], [t4].[renk], [t1].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t1].[oncelik], [t1].[tahmini_ucret], [t1].[olusturma_tarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
